Description:
You see a few water blobs playing in the agitated waters before the waterfalls.

One of them approaches you, it seems to be curious about your armor.

Surely if you give it an armor, the water blob will follow you for quite a while, but the armor will be lost. Perhaps you could try to befriend it in a less troublesome way.
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
